# Governance and CI files require maintainer approval.
# Prevents self-referential workflow bypass: a PR cannot modify
# review.yml to emit a fake passing review without maintainer sign-off.
# CODEOWNERS itself is protected to prevent a two-step bypass
# (remove protection in PR #A, then modify review.yml in PR #B).
.github/CODEOWNERS @edictum-ai/maintainers
.github/workflows/review.yml @edictum-ai/maintainers
.github/review-instructions.md @edictum-ai/maintainers
.github/review-template.md @edictum-ai/maintainers
CLAUDE.md @edictum-ai/maintainers
